Imported from http://haml.googlegroups.com/web/haml_highlighting_for_kde.tar.gz
based on http://haml-lang.com/editors.html

To install in you home:
  mkdir -p ~/.kde/share/apps/katepart/syntax/
  curl https://raw.github.com/ouvrages/haml_kate/master/haml.xml -o ~/.kde/share/apps/katepart/syntax/haml.xml

Then restart Kate and save your already open HAML files.
